  "rulesGoalBody": "Race to 20 victory points: complete colour groups, own conglomerate tiles and utilities, and hold the most cash each round. Reach the target and the game ends at once.",
  "rulesMoveTitle": "Moving",
  "rulesMoveBody": "No dice. Play a value from your velocity hand to advance; it refills when empty. Passing Go still pays a salary.",
  "rulesAuctionTitle": "Sealed-bid auctions",
  "rulesAuctionBody": "Land on an unowned tile and every player bids at once in a short sealed-bid window. The highest bid wins; the discoverer has the edge on ties. Bid 0 to abstain.",
  "rulesBuildTitle": "Building & rent",
  "rulesBuildBody": "Build houses evenly across a full colour group to raise rent; a full unimproved group already charges double. Mortgage tiles for quick cash - but a mortgaged tile is a cheap buyout target for rivals.",
  "rulesJailTitle": "Jail",
  "rulesJailBody": "Escape by choice, not dice: play a Legal Route (a fresh ordered hand), bribe your way out (opponents vote), or spend a jail card. While your Legal Route lasts, your tiles charge no rent.",
  "rulesWinTitle": "Winning",
  "rulesWinBody": "Win by points, by being the last player still solvent, or - in timed games - by being the richest when the clock runs out.",

